{"tid":1896824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「丟下一萬元就跑」洗版  中共炮製煽情假新聞維穩","createTime":"2020-02-25T11:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T12:17:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e316d012d32e9a886c534bd798c50a122bcacb6","tid":1896824,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/Z5KNIOAPSIKOZCQFPMBI4CHAWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FZ5KNIOAPSIKOZCQFPMBI4CHAWE%2F&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=1cfec534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200225%2FZ5KNIOAPSIKOZCQFPMBI4CHAWE%2F&h=1da7f1d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200225/Z5KNIOAPSIKOZCQFPMBI4CHAWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n「丟下一萬元就跑」洗版 <br />\n中共炮製煽情假新聞維穩<br />\n<br />\n內地政府封鎖消息導致疫情大爆發，同時全面開動宣傳機器，炮製溫情感人的抗疫故事。先是有女醫護集體剪髮、孕婦醫護上前線等「暖新聞」，再有各地「不約而同」出現熱心市民在公安局門外「丟下一萬元就跑」的報道，以煽情掩蓋死難。時事評論員認為，中共高層為顧及經濟，要創造疫情受控、好轉的假象以圖維穩。<br />\n<br />\n自疫情浮面開始，內地當局已要求加強正面宣傳。近期成為熱話、女醫護剃頭髮上前線的新聞，先由甘肅發出，之後河南、陝西也有類似的報道；上月也有懷孕多周的女醫護不顧安危，爭相前往疫區支援的新聞。最教人嘖嘖稱奇的是，有內地網友整理「丟下就跑新聞匯總」，由網上及搜索引擎的點擊發現，全國各地都有人在公安局外「丟下一萬元就跑」。這些善心舉動的報道，被質疑是官方造假文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200225/large/1582560522_3015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200225%2Flarge%2F1582560522_3015.jpg&h=31011676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習早前戴口罩在北京指揮防疫工作。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n派300記者發掘「好人好事」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港發紅旅警 撤300旅團<br />\n<br />\n事實上，中共「刀把子」之稱的中央政法委上周二發通知，要求各地要深入挖掘動人事迹，「推出更多有溫度、有淚點的『暖新聞』」。在通知第二日，經營7年多的敢言自媒體「大家」被註銷賬號，其上月曾發表文章批評疫情是「全體中國人都在承受媒體死亡的代價」。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹指出，中共高層顧及經濟，要創造疫情受控、好轉的假象，讓企業可放心復工。早前更派出300名記者到武漢，發掘好人好事、軟性新聞，大肆報道各地復工率。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n===================<br />\n<br />\n記得睇埋動新聞，好好笑。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367749a3671b4b643bcaf1011f3c34ddca16ccd2","tid":1896824,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"煽情呢d垃圾tvb日日播緊啦<br />\n不停洗垃圾腦"},{"pid":"e08059d84b633400934d938cb1804fac4823252c","tid":1896824,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"俾埋動新聞 link 啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://d2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net/appledaily/import/2020/02/24/5e541d2946e0fb0009e77ec3/20200224_chi_25nAD_w.mp4?player=powa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net%2Fappledaily%2Fimport%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2F5e541d2946e0fb0009e77ec3%2F20200224_chi_25nAD_w.mp4%3Fplayer%3Dpowa&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=e2816715\" target=\"_blank\">https://d2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net/appledaily/import/2020/02/24/5e541d2946e0fb0009e77ec3/20200224_chi_25nAD_w.mp4?player=powa</a>"},{"pid":"3b8fb5d1f1d5a365e77dc0b0cf5e096f8d77b155","tid":1896824,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rC0vt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rC0vt7.jpg&h=ee260f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d810385b166ebb28cfdc362bdd6ae9bb07b02dfc","tid":1896824,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"習近平死左可能有用d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d90fbef79fb4838d9abdd7f4e12f24939cd3238","tid":1896824,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"咁有錢既一早走哂啦，仲留低丟下一萬元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0